---
title: Sticky Asian Veggie Mince Stir-Fry & Garlic Rice with Asian Greens & Crushed Peanuts
description: A stir-fry sauce can do no wrong, in fact it’s perfection when cooked with veggie mince, creating lovely sticky flavours.
There’s veggies and a fragrant garlic rice to absorb all the leftover sauce. It’s too good to miss!
